<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-05-01T18:26:40-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-05-01T18:26:40-04:00</published><updated> 2024-05-01T18:26:40-04:00</updated><title> Snapchat 很快将允许您在发送后编辑消息</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;snapchat功能的三张截图&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/80ft6pSmAspHulhc7W-k1lKGWY4=/0x0:1482x988/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/ uploads/chorus_image/image/73321442/May_Bundle_Newsroom_Image.0.jpeg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;编辑消息、AI Bitmoji 时尚和提醒完善了新的 Snapchat 更新。&lt;/em>; |图片：Snap&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;nAEK2s&quot;>;Snap 正在推出&lt;a href=&quot;https://newsroom.snap.com/new-features-may-2024&quot;>;一系列新功能Snapchat 中的功能&lt;/a>;，包括编辑已发送消息的功能，允许您纠正“您的”与“您是”的拼写错误或其他令人尴尬的错误。 Snapchat 还获得了表情符号反应、地图反应和新的人工智能提醒功能。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;TnGrmD&quot;>;编辑消息功能的窗口期很短：您需要在发送后五分钟内采取行动- 并且仅当收件人尚未打开它时。 Snap 表示，该功能将“首先”向 Snapchat Plus 订阅者提供——这一决定与埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/6/6/23751962/twitter- 上的相同功能付费专区相呼应。 edit-tweet-limit-extended-60-分钟-blue-subscribers&quot;>;Twitter Blue&lt;/a>; (&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/27/23935317/x-premium -basic-subscriptions-reply-boost-no-ads&quot;>;现在称为 X Premium&lt;/a>;），成立于一年多前。&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;GIF：Snap &lt;/cite>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;K45S6z&quot;>;发送后消息编辑是消息应用程序中一项蓬勃发展的功能，...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https:/ /www.theverge.com/2024/5/1/24146618/snapchat-message-edit-plus-feature-map-reactions-ai-reminders-bitmoji-fashion&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/1/24146618/snapchat-message-edit-plus-feature-map-reactions-ai-reminders-bitmoji-fashion" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/1/24146618/snapchat-message-edit-plus-feature-map-reactions-ai-reminders-bitmoji-fashion</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-05-01T17:53:41-04:00</published><updated> 2024-05-01T17:53:41-04:00</updated><title> UnitedHealth 首席执行官承认向 BlackCat 支付了 2200 万美元赎金</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;许多光标指向笔记本电脑上一张不高兴的脸&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/s_dK5OkbPvoMwlHZz7oBzrOHpPk=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox -cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73321389/akrales_220309_4977_0182.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;1mKwah&quot;>;健康保险提供商 UnitedHealth 向黑客支付了数百万美元的赎金，这些黑客&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/29/24087105/united-health-black-cat-ransom-ware-hospitals- payments&quot;首席执行官安德鲁·威蒂(Andrew Witty)周三证实，>;闯入了其子公司之一&lt;/a>;，几个月来扰乱了全国各地的医疗保健提供商。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;ebaLuG&quot;>;在参议院财政委员会举行的听证会上，威蒂表示支付 2200 万美元赎金完全是他的决定。 “这是我做过的最艰难的决定之一，”他说。联合健康&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.cnbc.com/2024/04/22/unitedhealth-paid-ransom-to-bad-actors-says-病人-data-was-compromished-in-change-healthcare- cyberattack.html&quot;>;上个月承认&lt;/a>;，它已向破坏 Change Healthcare 系统（该系统由 UnitedHealth 拥有）的黑客支付了赎金，但没有透露具体金额。 3 月份，该公司&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/29/24087105/united-health-black-cat-ransom-ware-hospitals- payments&quot;>;将此次违规行为归咎于 BlackCat &lt;/a>;，也是对拉斯维加斯米高梅赌场黑客事件负责的同一实体。同月，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.wired.com/story/alphv-change-healthcare-ransomware- payment/&quot;>;&lt;em>;...&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;&lt;/ p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/1/24146693/unitedhealth-22-million-ransom-ransomware-hack-blackcat&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/1/24146693/unitedhealth-22-million-ransom-ransomware-hack-blackcat" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/1/24146693/unitedhealth-22-million-ransom-ransomware-hack-blackcat</id><author><name>盖比·德尔·瓦莱</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-05-01T16:27:17-04:00</published><updated> 2024-05-01T16:27:17-04:00</updated><title>就像所有其他主播一样，Crunchyroll 的价格将会变得更高一些</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;类似漫画的插图，一个红发女孩，扎着长马尾辫，穿着短袖和服式连衣裙。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/X7nvuFNkF1YU3FNZ0nkOCYWUUtI=/0x55:916x666/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73321162/hime.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Crunchyroll&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;r6WeQV&quot;>;而&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/26/24081180/crunchyroll-president- purini-anime-funimation-shutdown-sony-merger-decoder-interview&quot;>;Crunchyroll 的每月价格五年来没有上涨，索尼正准备为少数国家/地区的订阅者改变这种情况。&lt;/p >; &lt;p id=&quot;ozLzI1&quot;>;Crunchyroll &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crunchyroll.com%2Fnews%2Fannouncements %2F2024%2F5%2F1%2Fcrunchyroll-premium-price-updates-mega-ultimate-fan&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F5%2F1%2F24146651%2Fcrunchyroll -price-increase-subscription-anime&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;今天宣布&lt;/a>;，由于“公司对更多动漫、音乐和游戏等附加服务以及额外订户福利的投资。”虽然基本的 Crunchyroll Premium 价格仍为 7.99 美元/月，但 Mega Fan 级别的订阅价格将从 9.99 美元/月上涨至 11.99 美元/月，Ultimate Fan 级别将从 14.99 美元/月上涨至 15.99 美元/月。 &lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;nvfmWG&quot;>;Crunchyroll 还将免费试用期从两周缩短至一周。值得注意的是，价格...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/1/24146651/crunchyroll-price-increase-subscription-anime&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip ;&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/1/24146651/crunchyroll-price-increase-subscription-anime" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/1/24146651/c